<p style=" margin-top:0px; margin-bottom:0px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px;">Solomon chooses the identity of Preacher. It's believed that the reason he uses this title is because he is saying he has returned to God after years and years of idolatry. He also puts it before the title of king because he is emphasizing that it is more important than that title.</p></body></html>